de.schlegel11.jfxanimation

Class JFXAnimationTemplateAction<N,T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.schlegel11.jfxanimation.JFXAnimationTemplateAction<N,T>

  • public final class JFXAnimationTemplateAction<N,T>
extends Object
    Class which represents a builder and the configuration of animation keyframes. The configuration methods are based on the methods of a KeyFrame and KeyValue.
    It is possible that not all methods supported because the specific implementation of an animation can diverge from general KeyFrame and KeyValue implementations.
    Since:
    2018-09-22
    Author:
    Marcel Schlegel (schlegel11)
